race.comment: ZOU BIG BOY (2) loves this course and distance with two wins and two seconds from just five attempts and looks to be building up to another victory. Must be respected out of the Gollan camp and should be right there at the business end. MORE TROUBLE (1) has hit the top-four in all three runs this campaign and Thornton sticks in the stirrups. Can find winning form against this line-up. PELE PRINCESS (7) got a well-deserved win over this track and trip at the latest effort and will have derived some confidence from that victory. Can go back-to-back without surprising. SILENT CALL (5) is a last-start winner who looks to have some upside. In the mix. ZHENG YOU (6) best of the rest from the favourable draw.
